  <name>Brief</name>
  <summary>A GUI for tldr pages</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Brief is a GTK4 application for browsing tldr-pages. It provides a clean, native
      interface to view community-maintained help pages for command-line tools.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Built with GTK4 and Libadwaita for a seamless GNOME experience.</li>
      <li>Works offline with cached pages.</li>
      <li>Filter platform-specific commands (Linux, Windows, Android, etc.).</li>
      <li>Browse commands in multiple languages.</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <developer id="io.github.shonebinu">
